12.0pt;font-family:宋体; color:black'&gt;n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-ansi-language:FR'&gt;项和&lt;span lang=FR style='position:relative;top:6.0pt;mso-text-raise:-6.0pt'&gt;&lt;img width=49 height=25 src=&quot;/Public/tikupics/20151126/06/13/56578426327db1448576038.gif&quot; v:shapes=&quot;_x0000_i1026&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;，则&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体; color:black'&gt;a9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-ansi-language:FR'&gt;的值为&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;（&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;&lt;span style='mso-spacerun:yes'&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;）&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;  ";s:6:"clicks";N;s:11:"source_name";s:75:"2015-2016学年宁夏育才中学高二上期中考试数学（文）试题";s:13:"difficulty_id";s:1:"2";}i:4;a:6:{s:2:"id";s:5:"54962";s:7:"options";s:521:"["<img width=70 height=24 src=\"\/Public\/tikupics\/20151126\/06\/13\/56578426ac5dc1448576038.gif\" v:shapes=\"Picture_x0020_2\">","<img width=57 height=26 src=\"\/Public\/tikupics\/20151126\/06\/13\/56578426c706c1448576038.gif\" v:shapes=\"Picture_x0020_3\">","<img width=49 height=26 src=\"\/Public\/tikupics\/20151126\/06\/13\/56578426e1afc1448576038.gif\" v:shapes=\"Picture_x0020_4\">","<img width=59 height=26 src=\"\/Public\/tikupics\/20151126\/06\/13\/565784270465c1448576039.gif\" v:shapes=\"Picture_x0020_5\">"]";s:7:"content";s:470:" &lt;span style='font-size: 11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;数列&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;&lt;img width=111 height=21 src=&quot;/Public/tikupics/20151126/06/13/565784269583b1448576038.gif&quot; v:shapes=&quot;Picture_x0020_1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;的一个通项公式是（&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;&lt;span style='mso-spacerun:yes'&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;）&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;  ";s:6:"clicks";N;s:11:"source_name";s:75:"2015-2016学年宁夏育才中学高二上期中考试数学（理）试题";s:13:"difficulty_id";s:1:"2";}i:5;a:6:{s:2:"id";s:5:"54963";s:7:"options";s:17:"["1","2","3","4"]";s:7:"content";s:5312:" &lt;span style='font-size: 11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;若存在正整数&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;，对于任意正整数&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;n&lt;/span&gt;都有&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black; position:relative;top:6.0pt;mso-text-raise:-6.0pt'&gt;&lt;img width=60 height=24 src=&quot;/Public/tikupics/20151126/06/13/565784273219d1448576039.gif&quot; v:shapes=&quot;_x0000_i1025&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;成立，则称数列&lt;span lang=EN-US style='position:relative;top:6.0pt;mso-text-raise:-6.0pt'&gt;&lt;img width=31 height=24 src=&quot;/Public/tikupics/20151126/06/13/5657842748f3d1448576039.gif&quot; v:shapes=&quot;_x0000_i1026&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;为周期数列，周期为&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;，已知数列&lt;span lang=EN-US style='position:relative;top:6.0pt; mso-text-raise:-6.0pt'&gt;&lt;img width=31 height=24 src=&quot;/Public/tikupics/20151126/06/13/5657842748f3d1448576039.gif&quot; v:shapes=&quot;_x0000_i1027&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;满足：&lt;span lang=EN-US style='position:relative;top:6.0pt;mso-text-raise:-6.0pt'&gt;&lt;img width=92 height=24 src=&quot;/Public/tikupics/20151126/06/13/565784277a76d1448576039.gif&quot; v:shapes=&quot;_x0000_i1028&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;，&lt;span lang=EN-US style='position:relative;top:24.0pt;mso-text-raise:-24.0pt'&gt;&lt;img width=136 height=72 src=&quot;/Public/tikupics/20151126/06/13/565784279150d1448576039.gif&quot; v:shapes=&quot;_x0000_i1029&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;，关于下列命题：&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left'&gt;&lt;span style='font-size: 11.0pt;